Package adrenaline.network.rmi

Interface RmiClientCallbackInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RmiClient
    public interface RmiClientCallbackInterface
extends java.rmi.Remote
    Interface that declares methods callable by the RMI server on a RMI client, it is used by the server to identify each client
